docs.text: Contributing Guidelines ¶ 随时欢迎任何人提交Pull Request，或者在GitHub上提交Issue。 科研仔在科研过程中遇到的问题也可以提在Issue里，对于有价值的提问，我们会整理归纳成文档。 项目文件目录： . ├── docs # 文档目录 ├── Makefile ├── mkdocs.yml # 配置文件，定义了文档的总体目录、远程库位置和视觉主题 ├── README.md # 项目介绍 └── requirements.txt # 用于安装依赖的Python包 下载此库至本地，并进入目录: git clone https://github.com/kyzjnbk/kyzjnbk cd kyzjnbk 环境配置(需要python 3.x)： pip3 install -r ./requirements.txt 在本地实时预览(默认8000端口)： mkdocs serve 基本排版 ¶ Markdown Reference Material for MkDocs - Reference 多媒体 ¶ 图片 图片 Markdown源码 说明 ![](contributing.asserts/avril.png) ![](path_to_image) Youtube视频 Youtube视频 Markdown源码 说明 ![ type:video ]( https://www.youtube.com/embed/8xg3vE8Ie_E ) ![ type:video ]( https://www.youtube.com/embed/video_id ) BiliBili视频 BiliBili视频 HTML源码 说明 < iframe src = "//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=60825989&bvid=BV1kt411A7mK&cid=105846665&page=1" scrolling = "no" border = "0" frameborder = "no" framespacing = "0" allowfullscreen = "true" style = "width: 100%; height: 500px; max-width: 100%；align:center; padding:20px 0;" > </ iframe > 复制嵌入代码后加上 style="width: 100%; height: 500px; max-width: 100%；align:center; padding:20px 0;" Jupyter Notebook ¶ Google Colab Google Colab Markdown HTML 说明 The markdown for the badge is the following: [ ![Open In Colab ]( https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg )](https://colab.research.google.com/github/googlecolab/colabtools/blob/master/notebooks/colab-github-demo.ipynb) The HTML equivalent is: < a href = "https://colab.research.google.com/github/googlecolab/colabtools/blob/master/notebooks/colab-github-demo.ipynb" > < img src = "https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg" alt = "Open In Colab" /> </ a > 图标URL： https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg 链接格式： https://colab.research.google.com/github/ORGNAZATION_NAME/REPO_NAME/blob/BRANCH_NAME/PATH_TO_NOTEBOOK
